                                "stop": 16.213,
                                "byte_start": 100542,
                                "byte_stop": 165430,
                                "text": "The judgment and opinion of the Court in 75-1344, Scarborough against the United States and 76-451, Alabama Power Company against Davis will each be announced by Mr. Justice Marshall."
                            }
                        ]
                    },
                    {
                        "start": 16.213,
                        "stop": 96.717,
